Tim Barrett (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_Barrett_(actor) 0 Tim Barrett (31 May 1929 – 20 August 1990) was an English actor best remembered for playing Malcolm Harris, Terry's boss, in Series 3–7 of the classic UK sitcom Terry and June.
